Write a program that asks the user for a weight in kilograms and converts it to pounds. There are 2.2 pounds in a kilogram. 
# Program to convert weight from kilograms to pounds  
# Input weight in kilograms
kg = float(input("Enter weight in kilograms: "))  
# Conversion formula 
pounds = kg * 2.2 # 
Display result  
print(f"{kg} kilograms is equal to {pounds:.2f} pounds.")  

